[30;1m132 | [0m[35mwhere 168 is the length of time series and ``n_regions_extracted`` is the number of[0m
[30;1m133 | [0m[35mextracted regions. Likewise, we have a total of 20 subject specific time series signals.[0m

[30;1m63 | [0m[35mwith excessive motion (frame displacement greater than 0.5 mm). A minimum[0m

[30;1m7 | [0m[35m:term:`FREM` uses an implicit spatial regularization through fast clustering[0m

[30;1m902 | [0m[35msuch as ``get_dataset_dir`` to find a directory where the dataset is or will be[0m
[30;1m903 | [0m[35mstored according to the user's configuration, or ``fetch_files`` to load files[0m
[30;1m904 | [0m[35mfrom the disk or download them if they are missing.[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m1229[0m[34m of [0m[33m2184[0m[31m ]--[0m

[30;1m888 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m889 | [0m[35mDownloading data takes time and large datasets slow down the build of the[0m
[30;1m890 | [0m[35mexample gallery. Moreover, downloads can fail for reasons we do not control,[0m
[30;1m891 | [0m[35msuch as a web service that is temporarily unavailable. This is frustrating for[0m
[30;1m892 | [0m[35musers and a major issue for continuous integration (new code cannot be merged[0m
[30;1m893 | [0m[35munless the examples run successfully on the CI infrastructure). Finally,[0m
[30;1m894 | [0m[35mdatasets or the APIs that provide them sometimes change, in which case the[0m

[30;1m152 | [0m[35m        permutation computation.[0m
[30;1m153 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m128 | [0m[35m    scores_as_ranks_part : array-like, shape=(n_regressors, n_descriptors)[0m
[30;1m129 | [0m[35m        The ranks of the original scores in ``h0_fmax_part``.[0m

[30;1m224 | [0m[35mA well-known issue that arises here is that of multiple comparisons:[0m
[30;1m225 | [0m[35mwhen a statistical tests is repeated a large number times, say one for each voxel,[0m
[30;1m226 | [0m[35mi.e. ``n_voxels`` times, then one can expect that, in the absence of any effect, the number of detec[0m
[30;1m227 | [0m[35mfalse detections since there is no effect -- will be roughly :math:`n\_voxels*\alpha`.[0m
[30;1m228 | [0m[35mIf :math:`\alpha=.001` and :math:`n=10^5`, the number of false detections will be about 100.[0m
[30;1m229 | [0m[35mThe danger is that one may no longer trust the detections,[0m

[30;1m179 | [0m[35mHowever, if we assume that the noise is Gaussian and that the model is correctly specified,[0m
[30;1m180 | [0m[35mthen we know that ``t`` should follow a Student distribution with ``dof`` degrees of freedom,[0m
[30;1m181 | [0m[35mwhere ``dof`` is the number of free parameters in the model:[0m
[30;1m182 | [0m[35min practice, the number of observations (i.e. the number of time points), ``n_scans``[0m

[30;1m184 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m185 | [0m[35m :math:`dof = n\_scans - n\_columns`[0m

[30;1m101 | [0m[35msimply stated, it measures how the shape of one function's plot affects the shape of another functio[0m
[30;1m102 | [0m[35m**Remark:** it assumes linearity of the :term:`BOLD` response,[0m
[30;1m103 | [0m[35man assumption that may be wrong in some scenarios).[0m
[30;1m104 | [0m[35mIt is this predicted time course, also known as a *predictor*,[0m
[30;1m105 | [0m[35mthat is compared to the actual :term:`fMRI` signal.[0m
[30;1m106 | [0m[35mIf the correlation between the predictor and the signal is higher than expected by chance,[0m
[30;1m107 | [0m[35mthe voxel is said to exhibit a significant response to the event type.[0m

[30;1m76 | [0m[35m**Caching** In practice the implementation of :term:`Ward clustering` first[0m
[30;1m77 | [0m[35mcomputes a tree of possible merges, and then, given a requested number of[0m
[30;1m78 | [0m[35mclusters, breaks apart the tree at the right level.[0m
[30;1m79 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m80 | [0m[35mAs the tree is independent of the number of clusters, we can rely on caching to speed things up when[0m
[30;1m81 | [0m[35mnumber of clusters. In Wards clustering,[0m
